(345, NULL, 'Apple IPhone 7 Plus 5.5&#039;&#039; Inch 128GB+3GB', 'https://www.domarket.com.ng/assets/images/products/1577369578wpeadeqfsbixdrcnxfmalnwyqhbnbzszmwtd61AC6EA6-F899-45E5-9014-C00247D8BE71.jpeg', 'https://www.domarket.com.ng/assets/images/products/1577369578wsdfbfesdqhwpebmlzrnmiqtcaxbwnydzxanA18D6891-D877-4355-8CD5-960E67D66C78.jpeg', 'https://www.domarket.com.ng/assets/images/products/1577369578elydzwtzcmwnbxnpdqqimafenxwbsbdahrfs2BFD231C-2FBC-4087-B093-E692EC08A7D2.jpeg', 'https://www.domarket.com.ng/assets/images/products/1577369578mqwbxnxpirzdznhysnafdwbscdtmwafebelq263A17A8-3DFB-4D90-96FC-1A24EFD40C92.jpeg', NULL, NULL, 4, 26400, 166900, '&lt;p&gt;Apple iPhone 7 Plus was launched in May 2017 &amp;amp; runs on iOS 11. The Smartphone is available in more than three color options i.e.Black, Rose Gold, Jet Black, Silver &amp;amp; has a built in fingerprint sensor as the primary security feature, along with the host of connectivity options in terms of 3G, 4G, GPS, Wifi, NFC Bluetooth capabilities. Priced at Rs. 49999 the phone comes in 32GB &amp;amp; 128GB variants.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Smartphone is powered by 2.34 GHz Quad core A10 Processor. A 3 GB of RAM ensures phone runs smoothly even the most memory intensive applications &amp;amp; still shows no signs of lag. 32GB &amp;amp; 128GB of internal storage options can not be expanded further.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Phone comes with a 2900 mAh battery to support it&#039;s 5.5 inch screen with LED-backlit IPS LCD, capacitive touchscreen, display having a resolution of 1080 x 1920 at 401 ppi. The screen is also protected by a durable Scratch Resistant glass.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Apple iPhone 7 Plus boasts of dual primary camera of 12 + 12 MP megapixel and 7 megapixel front Camera. The Smartphone is also loaded with Optical Image Stablization and has a low camera aperture of 1.8. It also supports Face Detection and high dynamic range(HDR) imaging.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;section class=&quot;col8 card _fw -pvs -mvxs -fs12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;markup -oxa -pas&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;iPhone 7 Plus&amp;nbsp;Technical Details&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Display&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;5.5-inch Retina HD display&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Capacity&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;128GB&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Splash, Water, and Dust Resistant&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Water and dust resistant (rated IP67)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Camera &amp;amp; Video&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Dual 12MP cameras with Portrait mode, HDR, and 4K video at 30 fps&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Front Camera&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;7MP FaceTime HD camera with HDR&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Power and Battery&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Talk time (wireless): Up to 21 hours; Internet use: Up to 13 hours; Video playback (wireless): Up to 14 hours; Audio playback (wireless): Up to 60 hours&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Height&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;6.23 inches (158.2 mm)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Width&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;3.07 inches (77.9 mm)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;D&lt;strong&gt;epth&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;0.29 inch (7.3 mm)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Weight&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;6.63 ounces (188 grams)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n&lt;section class=&quot;col8 card _fw -pvs -mvxs -fs12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 class=&quot;-m -fs14 -phs&quot;&gt;Key Features&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;markup -pas&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;High quality refurbished by Strictly tested, Powerful battery.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A gift of 1*screen protector, 1*phone case&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Screen: 5.5 inches LED-backlit IPS LCD&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Memory: 3GB RAM, 128GB Memory&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;CPU: Quad-core 2.23 GHz&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Camera: 12MP Wide Angle rear cameras, 7MP Front Camera&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n&lt;section class=&quot;col8 card _fw -pvs -mvxs -fs12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 class=&quot;-m -fs14 -phs&quot;&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s in the box&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;markup -pas&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;1 x phone&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;1 x headphone&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;1 x charger( with cable),&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;1 x&amp;nbsp; phone case&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;1 x&amp;nbsp; screen protector&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n&lt;section class=&quot;col8 card _fw -pvs -mvxs -fs12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 class=&quot;-m -fs14 -phs&quot;&gt;Display&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;-pas&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;-m&quot;&gt;Screen Size:&lt;/span&gt; 5.5&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n&lt;section class=&quot;col8 card _fw -pvs -mvxs -fs12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 class=&quot;-m -fs14 -phs&quot;&gt;Storage &amp;amp; Speed&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;-pas&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;-m&quot;&gt;ROM (internal storage):&lt;/span&gt; 32&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;-m&quot;&gt;RAM:&lt;/span&gt; 3&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n&lt;section class=&quot;col8 card _fw -pvs -mvxs -fs12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 class=&quot;-m -fs14 -phs&quot;&gt;Operating System&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;-pas&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;-m&quot;&gt;Operating Syste