(364, NULL, 'Samsung Galaxy Note 10 (8gb+ 256GB) 6.3&#039;&#039', 'https://www.domarket.com.ng/assets/images/products/1577553987wnzxzadlawfnctbqdbdwsimrbemsqfnyxehpA3ACAAD5-C828-42AC-B349-3F05F015C529.jpeg', 'https://www.domarket.com.ng/assets/images/products/1577553988lptqawdzsbmbzqnrexwnamyddbnxhfesfiwcA10F5D02-D957-47CF-8D80-62AB1ABB38C4.jpeg', 'https://www.domarket.com.ng/assets/images/products/1577553988zenbfcfmxdmwbaayishxntplwqqdnberzswd16E5771B-73D4-43C1-8D79-9AF9EEFD8739.jpeg', 'https://www.domarket.com.ng/assets/images/products/1577553988hpszdyelfsminnnddabbbcwxqwzetmqwfrxa4238AF2A-24D0-49C1-8F7D-24F98365A6EC.jpeg', NULL, NULL, 3, 310000, 280000, '&lt;h4 class=&quot;a-spacing-mini&quot;&gt;Power that lasts more than your day.&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;An all-day battery that intelligently powers every scroll, click, call, tap, playlist and season finale you can throw at it.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Based on average battery life under typical usage conditions. Average expected performance based on typical use. Actual battery life depends on factors such as network, features selected, frequency of calls, and voice, data, and other application usage patterns. Results may vary.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h4 class=&quot;a-spacing-mini&quot;&gt;Hours of power from minutes of charge.&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Charge up with Superfast Charge and head out the door faster, with more juice.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;When using the included charger and cable.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h4 class=&quot;a-spacing-mini&quot;&gt;Storage of a laptop in your pocket.&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Generous storage out of the box plus expandable* memory means you never have to delete what&amp;rsquo;s important to you.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;*Not available on Galaxy Note10; microSD card sold separately.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h4 class=&quot;a-spacing-mini&quot;&gt;Immersive, nearly bezel-less cinematic display.&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;With nearly immersive bezels, Galaxy Note10 cinema-quality display elevates everything you watch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;section class=&quot;col8 card _fw -pvs -mvxs -fs12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 class=&quot;-m -fs14 -phs&quot;&gt;Key Features&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;markup -pas&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Display -&amp;nbsp;6.3-inch Dynamic AMOLED, 2280x1080, HDR1+&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Operating System -&amp;nbsp;Android 9 Pie , One UI 1.5&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Processor -&amp;nbsp;Snapdragon 855&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Memory/Storage -&amp;nbsp;8GB/256GB&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Rear Camera -&amp;nbsp;(12MP, f/1.5-2.4, OIS, 77&amp;deg; FoV)+(16MP, f/2.2, 123&amp;deg; FoV)+(12MP, f/2.1, OIS, 45&amp;deg; FoV)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Front Camera -&amp;nbsp;10MP, f/2.2, 80&amp;deg; FoV , auto focus&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Battery -&amp;nbsp;3500mAh , 25W wired, 12W wireless&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n&lt;section class=&quot;col8 card _fw -pvs -mvxs -fs12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 class=&quot;-m -fs14 -phs&quot;&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s in the box&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;markup -pas&quot;&gt;Samsung galaxy note 10Fast chargercharging corduser manual&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n&lt;section class=&quot;col8 card _fw -pvs -mvxs -fs12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 class=&quot;-m -fs14 -phs&quot;&gt;Display&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;-pas&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;-m&quot;&gt;Screen Size:&lt;/span&gt; 6.3&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n&lt;section class=&quot;col8 card _fw -pvs -mvxs -fs12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 class=&quot;-m -fs14 -phs&quot;&gt;Operating System&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;-pas&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;-m&quot;&gt;Operating System:&lt;/span&gt; Windows 8.1&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n&lt;section class=&quot;col8 card _fw -pvs -mvxs -fs12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 class=&quot;-m -fs14 -phs&quot;&gt;Warranty&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;-pas&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;-m&quot;&gt;Product Warran