(365, NULL, 'Apple Airpod Pro', 'https://www.domarket.com.ng/assets/images/products/1577555191icaaxhdlqedezqmxynbtbbnrzsfdfswpwnwm3B97A195-9A2E-4A16-9D74-ACDEB59DBBB1.jpeg', 'https://www.domarket.com.ng/assets/images/products/1577555191flsqwfeaxzedmziwythmasbndnbpxdwnqrcb71931A87-41A4-4D6A-8381-E43F990A6905.jpeg', 'https://www.domarket.com.ng/assets/images/products/1577555191zprfmadlawwszxmynsiebxqhfwcqbbtdednn31E3F3A3-0ED4-415A-A935-2EEC40EF2F59.jpeg', NULL, NULL, NULL, 5, 12000, 114000, '&lt;p&gt;AirPods Pro have been designed to deliver Active Noise Cancellation for immersive sound, Transparency mode so you can hear your surroundings, and a customizable fit for all-day comfort. Just like AirPods, AirPods Pro connect magically to your iPhone or Apple Watch. And they&amp;rsquo;re ready to use right out of the case. Active Noise Cancellation Incredibly light noise-cancelling headphones, AirPods Pro block out your environment so you can focus on what you&amp;rsquo;re listening to. AirPods Pro use two microphones, an outward-facing microphone and an inward-facing microphone, to create superior noise cancellation. By continuously adapting to the geometry of your ear and the fit of the ear tips, Active Noise Cancellation silences the world to keep you fully tuned in to your music, podcasts, and calls. Transparency mode Switch to Transparency mode and AirPods Pro let the outside sound in, allowing you to hear and connect to your surroundings.&lt;/p&gt;', 10, 51, '2', 'Performance and specifications\r\n\r\nCondition â€” New\r\nBrand - Apple\r\nType - In-Ear\r\nConnectivity -     Wireless \r\nConnecting Interface -         Bluetooth \r\nColour -         White', 15, 0),
