(368, NULL, 'Galaxy SAMSUNG GALAXY A20s ( 3GB RAM, 32GB ROM) , ', 'https://www.domarket.com.ng/assets/images/products/1577593005wcbdzdwsbhlewnerfpimdxqytbmqxnnsafzaF8725526-C9E9-4826-BE50-5DD5C11AF42E.jpeg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 5, 70000, 62000, '&lt;section class=&quot;col8 card _fw -pvs -mvxs -fs12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;markup -oxa -pas&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Samsung Galaxy A20s comes with an affordable price-tag that is good for every consumer. The device has been provided with a tall display that features a waterdrop cut-out on the top. There is a decent set of the camera while the battery capacity of the device is sufficient to meet a one-day requirement. In terms of performance as well, the handset is provided with good processing front.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Display, Camera and Storage&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Samsung Galaxy A20s comes with a 6.5-inch IPS LCD display that bears a screen resolution of 1,520 x 720 pixels along with a pixel density of 259 PPI. It offers a decent viewing experience with the 19.5:9 aspect ratio but it lacks a full HD resolution.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;The camera of the smartphone is provided with 8MP and 5MP rear lenses, which features Bokeh Effect, Continuos Shooting, Exposure compensation, Face detection, Geo-tagging, High Dynamic Range mode (HDR), ISO control, Touch to focus, White balance presets. There is an 8MP front camera that captures excellent quality images with Autofocus and LED Flash.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;For the storage, the smartphone houses 64GB internal memory that can be expanded up to 512GB with the help of a microSD card.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Configuration and Battery&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Samsung Galaxy A20s is equipped with 1.8GHz octa-core processor, which is set on a Qualcomm Snapdragon 450 chipset. It has an Adreno 506 GPU and a 4GB RAM, which together ensure smooth and efficient multitasking.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;To draw power, the device has a Li-ion battery with 4,000mAh capacity, which gets fast charging technology. The battery is enough to provide a day of power backup while the fast charging technology helps to refill it in a very short time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Connectivity and more&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Samsung Galaxy A20s comes with a wide range of connectivity options including WiFi, 2G, VoLTE (Works with Jio), 4G LTE (India Compatible), Bluetooth, 3G, Micro USB, Mobile Hotspot, etc. Among the other features, it has Accelerometer, Proximity Sensor, Gyroscope, etc.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;rview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Samsung Galaxy A20s comes with an affordable price-tag that is good for every consumer. The device has been provided with a tall display that features a waterdrop cut-out on the top. There is a decent set of the camera while the battery capacity of the device is sufficient to meet a one-day requirement. In terms of performance as well, the handset is provided with good processing front.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Display, Camera and Storage&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Samsung Galaxy A20s comes with a 6.5-inch IPS LCD display that bears a screen resolution of 1,520 x 720 pixels along with a pixel density of 259 PPI. It offers a decent viewing experience with the 19.5:9 aspect ratio but it lacks a full HD resolution.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;The camera of the smartphone is provided with 8MP and 5MP rear lenses, which features Bokeh Effect, Continuos Shooting, Exposure compensation, Face detection, Geo-tagging, High Dynamic Range mode (HDR), ISO control, Touch to focus, White balance presets. There is an 8MP front camera that captures excellent quality images with Autofocus and LED Flash.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;For the storage, the smartphone houses 64GB internal memory that can be expanded up to 512GB with the help of a microSD card.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Configuration and Battery&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Samsung Galaxy A20s is equipped with 1.8GHz octa-core processor, which is set on a Qualcomm Snapdragon 450 chipset. It has an Adreno 506 GPU and a 4GB RAM, which together ensure smooth and efficient multitasking.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;To draw power, the device has a Li-ion battery with 4,000mAh capacity, which gets fast charging technology. The battery is enough to provide a day of power backup while the fast charging technology helps to refill it in a very short time.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Connectivity and more&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Samsung Galaxy A20s comes with a wide range of connectivity options including WiFi, 2G, VoLTE (Works with Jio), 4G LTE (India Compatible), Bluetooth, 3G, Micro USB, Mobile Hotspot, etc. Among the other features, it has Accelerometer, Proximity Sensor, Gyroscope, etc.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/section&gt;\r\n&lt;section class=&quot;col8 card _fw -pvs -mvxs -fs12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h2 class=&quot;-m -fs14 -phs&quot;&gt;Key Features&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;markup -pas&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot;keyspec p-h-l m-b-l&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;p-b-m br-b-1&quot;&gt;perating System\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot;m-t-s&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;Android v9.0 (Pie)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;p-b-m br-b-1&quot;&gt;Display\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot;m-t-s&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;6.5 inches (16.51 cm) bezel-less display with waterdrop notch&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/li&g